38
00:03:34,420 --> 00:03:35,390
What's wrong with you?

39
00:03:35,470 --> 00:03:36,700
Let me get you a blanket.

40
00:03:36,700 --> 00:03:37,470
Okay.

41
00:03:38,550 --> 00:03:40,790
