69
00:04:39,390 --> 00:04:40,430
Look at this.

70
00:04:40,450 --> 00:04:41,340
Madam Pei, it's late now.

71
00:04:41,340 --> 00:04:42,690
We have to report for school tomorrow.

72
00:04:44,020 --> 00:04:45,020
