75
00:04:48,340 --> 00:04:49,850
and will live in our house from now on.

76
00:04:49,900 --> 00:04:51,390
Take good care of her at school.

77
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:52,190
Do you hear me?

78
00:04:52,250 --> 00:04:53,900
