139
00:07:28,580 --> 00:07:29,120
Okay.

140
00:07:59,220 --> 00:08:01,070
She... She forgot her stuff.

141
00:08:02,390 --> 00:08:03,460
Xingruo.

142
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:04,510
Wait, you...

143
00:08:05,020 --> 00:08:05,950
Xingruo, wait a minute.

144
00:08:05,950 --> 00:08:08,630
Come on in.

145
00:08:09,140 --> 00:08:11,190
Come on, sit down.

146
00:08:13,870 --> 00:08:14,820
What are you doing?

147
00:08:14,950 --> 00:08:16,950
I don't agree to be
on the show with him.

148
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:17,510
Xingruo,

149
00:08:17,510 --> 00:08:19,550
it's not a matter
of whether you agree or not.

150
00:08:20,070 --> 00:08:21,780
If I were a friend or a boss,

151
00:08:21,780 --> 00:08:22,950
I wouldn't want to push you.

152
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:25,580
The point is that Mr. Yang
sent me a voice message.

153
00:08:28,260 --> 00:08:30,460
Zhang, you're amazing.

154
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,950
I asked Shen to find an influencer,

155
00:08:31,950 --> 00:08:33,630
but she turned herself into one.

156
00:08:34,580 --> 00:08:36,220
My daughters and her classmates

157
00:08:36,220 --> 00:08:37,870
used to like Double-Star Team.

158
00:08:38,180 --> 00:08:39,940
They're all excited this morning.

159
00:08:40,710 --> 00:08:41,990
We need both of them

160
00:08:41,990 --> 00:08:43,510
on this show.

161
00:08:45,300 --> 00:08:46,180
Did you hear that?

162
00:08:46,660 --> 00:08:48,020
The investor has given his order.

163
00:08:48,300 --> 00:08:49,350
It's impossible.

164
00:08:50,140 --> 00:08:51,180
There's one more.

165
00:08:53,060 --> 00:08:54,260
No matter what,

166
00:08:54,390 --> 00:08:55,540
I want these two.

167
00:08:59,710 --> 00:09:01,710
Xingruo, just try it.

168
00:09:01,780 --> 00:09:02,940
To save money,

169
00:09:02,940 --> 00:09:04,360
we even laid off our cleaning staff.

170
00:09:04,660 --> 00:09:06,470
Besides, I've been defending the pay

171
00:09:06,470 --> 00:09:07,990
of those employees.

172
00:09:08,020 --> 00:09:09,420
If we don't pass this hurdle,

173
00:09:09,420 --> 00:09:11,470
there's really no tomorrow
for our company.

174
00:09:11,780 --> 00:09:13,940
I'm the producer of the show.

175
00:09:13,940 --> 00:09:15,830
There's no precedent on the market
for a producer

176
00:09:15,830 --> 00:09:17,230
to take part in a romance variety show.

177
00:09:17,230 --> 00:09:18,260
It's inappropriate.

178
00:09:18,660 --> 00:09:19,990
And even if I agree,

179
00:09:19,990 --> 00:09:21,660
Lu Xingyan next door won't agree.

180
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:23,830
He's fine.

181
00:09:23,830 --> 00:09:24,940
He's very cooperative.

182
00:09:25,870 --> 00:09:27,260
As soon as he heard about the show,

183
00:09:27,260 --> 00:09:29,230
he came into the office early
in the morning to talk to me.

184
00:09:29,710 --> 00:09:31,420
Now all we need is for you to say yes.

185
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:32,540
Impossible.

186
00:09:34,540 --> 00:09:35,470
I'll take this.

187
00:09:38,540 --> 00:09:39,260
Hello.

188
00:09:40,510 --> 00:09:41,390
I told you

189
00:09:41,540 --> 00:09:43,590
to give me two more days
on the second installment.

190
00:09:43,710 --> 00:09:45,590
I've been busy with meetings

191
00:09:45,590 --> 00:09:46,780
with investors lately.

192
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:47,590
Do you know what the point is?

193
00:09:47,590 --> 00:09:49,780
The point is
that the finance executive is on leave.

194
00:09:49,890 --> 00:09:52,230
As soon as she gets to work,
I'll settle it for you, okay?

195
00:10:09,470 --> 00:10:10,060
I've heard

196
00:10:10,060 --> 00:10:12,230
that you're dying to be on our show.

197
00:10:12,300 --> 00:10:14,350
I've just gone out to make a preparation

198
00:10:14,510 --> 00:10:16,710
to give you the best briefing.

199
00:10:16,710 --> 00:10:18,540
Didn't you ask me to come?

200
00:10:21,420 --> 00:10:23,180
As the producer and director

201
00:10:23,390 --> 00:10:24,660
of this show,

202
00:10:24,990 --> 00:10:26,940
I'd really like you

203
00:10:26,940 --> 00:10:28,780
to come and join us.

204
00:10:29,990 --> 00:10:32,060
Come on, let me brief you.

205
00:10:32,350 --> 00:10:33,350
Our show

206
00:10:33,350 --> 00:10:36,350
is called Go Back Lover
and it's a romance variety show.

207
00:10:36,420 --> 00:10:38,750
Unlike other variety shows
on the market today,

208
00:10:38,750 --> 00:10:40,870
we focus on two keywords,

209
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:42,020
ex and first love,

210
00:10:42,020 --> 00:10:44,230
to make people feel nostalgic
about their youth

211
00:10:44,230 --> 00:10:45,420
and thus trigger empathy.

212
00:10:45,540 --> 00:10:47,350
So you're making this show

213
00:10:48,390 --> 00:10:49,830
to reminisce about your exes?

214
00:10:50,140 --> 00:10:52,390
Actually, you can't say that.

215
00:10:55,140 --> 00:10:56,230
Reminiscing about exes

216
00:10:56,260 --> 00:10:57,540
is just a gimmick.

217
00:10:58,550 --> 00:11:00,120
The most important thing about a product

218
00:11:00,130 --> 00:11:01,910
like reminiscence reality shows
is the positioning.

219
00:11:02,180 --> 00:11:04,230
There is no such show
on the market now,

220
00:11:04,350 --> 00:11:07,110
so we are differentiating
ourselves fundamentally

221
00:11:07,140 --> 00:11:08,660
so as to win at the starting line.

222
00:11:09,230 --> 00:11:11,230
I don't want to hear about the show.

223
00:11:11,300 --> 00:11:13,510
Since you want me
to be a guest on the show,

224
00:11:14,110 --> 00:11:15,510
I'd like to ask you

225
00:11:17,420 --> 00:11:19,060
what I can expect

226
00:11:20,260 --> 00:11:21,540
from this partnership.

227
00:11:23,780 --> 00:11:26,710
If you can join us on the show,

228
00:11:29,140 --> 00:11:32,110
we can bring you some promotional help

229
00:11:32,260 --> 00:11:33,990
for your resort.

230
00:11:41,020 --> 00:11:43,060
Our company has its own publicity team.

231
00:11:43,870 --> 00:11:46,020
I agree with what you said
about differentiation.

232
00:11:46,180 --> 00:11:47,260
May I ask

233
00:11:48,390 --> 00:11:50,510
what's the difference
between your publicity

234
00:11:51,230 --> 00:11:52,300
and ours?

235
00:11:57,750 --> 00:11:58,710
Sorry, Mr. Lu.

236
00:11:59,390 --> 00:12:00,470
As you were not

237
00:12:00,470 --> 00:12:02,390
in our consideration before,

238
00:12:02,510 --> 00:12:03,660
we have not

239
00:12:03,660 --> 00:12:05,750
discussed this issue in detail.

240
00:12:05,990 --> 00:12:08,140
If you are willing to take part
in our variety show,

241
00:12:08,300 --> 00:12:10,260
we can arrange
for the filming of the show

242
00:12:10,260 --> 00:12:11,660
to take place in your resort.

243
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:13,510
Variety shows take a long time to shoot

244
00:12:13,510 --> 00:12:14,830
and require a lot of scenes.

245
00:12:14,990 --> 00:12:17,300
We can show your resort's
special features and style

246
00:12:17,300 --> 00:12:19,510
thoroughly in the show.

247
00:12:19,630 --> 00:12:22,390
Besides, variety shows
have a very wide audience.

248
00:12:22,390 --> 00:12:23,590
I'm sure the broadcast

249
00:12:23,590 --> 00:12:25,180
will bring a lot of guests

250
00:12:25,180 --> 00:12:26,630
to your resort.

251
00:12:28,420 --> 00:12:30,350
You're a very professional producer.

252
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:31,750
For the sake of the show,

253
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:34,500
you's gone so far as to invite your ex
to join the romance variety show

254
00:12:34,510 --> 00:12:37,470
and display your past relationship
to the nation's 1.4 billion audience.

255
00:12:38,350 --> 00:12:40,020
You're so career-minded.

256
00:12:42,770 --> 00:12:43,990
Falling in love and breaking up

257
00:12:44,060 --> 00:12:46,420
is something
that every adult goes through.

258
00:12:47,140 --> 00:12:48,350
As long as you get over it,

259
00:12:49,590 --> 00:12:50,900
there's nothing to be afraid of.

260
00:12:55,470 --> 00:12:57,020
So you've gotten over it,

261
00:12:58,900 --> 00:12:59,590
right?

262
00:13:00,990 --> 00:13:01,830
Of course.

263
00:13:02,390 --> 00:13:04,390
I'm inviting you
to be a guest on the show

264
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:06,230
as an organizer.

265
00:13:06,230 --> 00:13:07,420
If you're interested...

266
00:13:07,420 --> 00:13:08,420
I'm not interested.

267
00:13:08,990 --> 00:13:10,630
I'm here today to tell you

268
00:13:10,750 --> 00:13:13,530
that everything about this show
should never be mentioned to me again.

269
00:13:14,590 --> 00:13:15,870
I'm not going to take part in it.

270
00:13:17,300 --> 00:13:19,230
I've got some work to do.
I have to go now.

271
00:13:32,420 --> 00:13:33,230
Mr. Lu.

272
00:13:34,780 --> 00:13:35,590
Lawyer Zhai?

273
00:13:36,110 --> 00:13:37,230
You're back so soon.

274
00:13:37,390 --> 00:13:39,990
Yeah, it's to save money
on accommodation.

275
00:13:40,140 --> 00:13:41,660
And I flew economy class.

276
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:43,990
As soon as I landed,
I was called back for a meeting.

277
00:13:43,990 --> 00:13:46,350
I've been going around the clock
for 36 hours.

278
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:47,710
It must be hard on you.

279
00:13:47,710 --> 00:13:48,470
How about this?

280
00:13:48,590 --> 00:13:50,230
When you're rich,

281
00:13:50,230 --> 00:13:53,260
you can hire me to be your full-time lawyer
at your resort

282
00:13:53,470 --> 00:13:55,510
so I don't have to be exploited
by a law firm.

283
00:13:55,510 --> 00:13:56,230
No problem.

284
00:13:56,750 --> 00:13:58,830
Will you arrange business class for me?

285
00:14:00,350 --> 00:14:01,140
Of course.

286
00:14:04,900 --> 00:14:05,630
What?

287
00:14:06,350 --> 00:14:07,590
One of your eyelashes fell out.

288
00:14:08,830 --> 00:14:10,590
You can't just let him go.

289
00:14:10,590 --> 00:14:11,390
If he wasn't interested,

290
00:14:11,390 --> 00:14:13,230
he wouldn't have made
the trip here, would he?

291
00:14:13,230 --> 00:14:14,350
Didn't he say that?

292
00:14:14,350 --> 00:14:16,350
He came here today
to reject me to my face.

293
00:14:16,390 --> 00:14:17,420
That's impossible.

294
00:14:17,750 --> 00:14:19,140
Or didn't you make that clear to him?

295
00:14:19,140 --> 00:14:20,590
How about this? I'll talk to him.

296
00:14:20,650 --> 00:14:21,590
Maybe there's a chance.

297
00:14:21,590 --> 00:14:23,750
I couldn't answer the questions
he asked me.

298
00:14:23,750 --> 00:14:24,710
He asked what good

299
00:14:24,710 --> 00:14:26,020
the show would do for his resort.

300
00:14:26,020 --> 00:14:27,060
I don't know.

301
00:14:27,140 --> 00:14:28,990
If you don't know, find out.

302
00:14:29,140 --> 00:14:30,750
- I...
- Let's split up.

303
00:14:31,020 --> 00:14:32,990
I'll talk to Mr. Yang
about the investment first.

304
00:14:43,970 --> 00:14:47,370
(Incoming Call: Zhai Jiajing)

305
00:14:47,940 --> 00:14:48,630
Hello.

306
00:14:49,540 --> 00:14:50,630
I was careless last night

307
00:14:50,630 --> 00:14:52,260
and I left the file in your office.

308
00:14:52,590 --> 00:14:54,230
Okay, I'll send it back to you.

309
00:14:54,710 --> 00:14:55,540
There's no rush.

310
00:14:55,660 --> 00:14:58,420
Finish your best man duties today.

311
00:14:58,780 --> 00:15:00,140
I'll hang up now. Bye.

312
00:15:05,940 --> 00:15:07,750
What... What's going on?

313
00:15:08,260 --> 00:15:09,780
Isn't he single?

314
00:15:28,300 --> 00:15:29,750
I told you you shouldn't have gone.

315
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:32,350
I don't know what you're talking about.

316
00:15:32,780 --> 00:15:34,660
Stop it!

317
00:15:34,900 --> 00:15:35,830
Stop it!

318
00:15:38,450 --> 00:15:39,470
We've known each other for years.

319
00:15:39,470 --> 00:15:40,630
I know you very well.

320
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:42,630
If you're happy, you plant flowers.
If you're not, you do weed.

321
00:15:43,110 --> 00:15:44,630
What happened? Tell me.

322
00:15:44,740 --> 00:15:46,230
What did Shen Xingruo want
to talk to you about?

323
00:15:47,140 --> 00:15:48,020
It's purely work.

324
00:15:48,870 --> 00:15:49,940
Nothing emotional.

325
00:15:51,420 --> 00:15:53,020
Did she really ask you to be a guest?

326
00:15:53,780 --> 00:15:54,750
I went there

327
00:15:55,420 --> 00:15:56,900
to make her give up on it.

328
00:15:57,510 --> 00:15:58,510
Nothing else?

329
00:16:01,630 --> 00:16:03,110
We have nothing more to say.

330
00:16:12,020 --> 00:16:14,020
Qin, you're good cook.

331
00:16:15,230 --> 00:16:16,660
Call Xingruo

332
00:16:16,660 --> 00:16:18,590
and ask where she is.
Why isn't she back yet?

333
00:16:19,020 --> 00:16:21,020
I just called her. Her line's busy.

334
00:16:21,540 --> 00:16:22,660
She's probably still busy.

335
00:16:24,110 --> 00:16:25,780
She's been really busy lately.

336
00:16:25,780 --> 00:16:27,390
I feel bad for her.

337
00:16:28,710 --> 00:16:29,870
The day I first got here,

338
00:16:29,870 --> 00:16:31,780
she told me she was having nightmares.

339
00:16:32,540 --> 00:16:34,420
I guess she dreamt
about her family again.

340
00:16:34,750 --> 00:16:35,830
What do you think

341
00:16:36,350 --> 00:16:38,780
happened to her family back then?

342
00:16:38,830 --> 00:16:39,900
After all these years,

343
00:16:39,900 --> 00:16:41,300
she still won't tell us.

344
00:16:41,660 --> 00:16:42,780
That's how she is.

345
00:16:42,780 --> 00:16:44,110
Don't you know?

346
00:16:44,300 --> 00:16:46,470
She keeps everything to herself.

347
00:16:46,780 --> 00:16:48,830
She carries all the stress by herself.

348
00:16:49,830 --> 00:16:51,590
I wish we could help her.

349
00:16:51,590 --> 00:16:53,230
- She's back.
- We don't even know

350
00:16:53,230 --> 00:16:54,590
if Lu Xingyan is single,

351
00:16:54,590 --> 00:16:56,260
and you want me to go
to the inn to investigate.

352
00:16:56,260 --> 00:16:57,710
Aren't we wasting our time?

353
00:16:58,180 --> 00:16:59,830
That's why we have to be prepared.

354
00:16:59,830 --> 00:17:01,060
If he's single,

355
00:17:01,060 --> 00:17:02,060
he's our

356
00:17:02,060 --> 00:17:03,830
most perfect choice for a guest.

357
00:17:03,940 --> 00:17:05,590
You must convince him.

358
00:17:05,660 --> 00:17:06,590
I got it.

359
00:17:06,590 --> 00:17:08,590
I went to the inn this afternoon.

360
00:17:08,870 --> 00:17:10,590
I'll sort out the information

361
00:17:10,590 --> 00:17:11,460
and we'll talk.

362
00:17:11,870 --> 00:17:13,110
Okay, no problem.

363
00:17:13,270 --> 00:17:14,030
I have to go now.

364
00:17:15,590 --> 00:17:17,350
All right, watch out. Watch your hands.

365
00:17:17,700 --> 00:17:19,220
You're awesome, Qin.

366
00:17:19,220 --> 00:17:21,030
You've cooked so much good food today.

367
00:17:23,030 --> 00:17:24,130
What were you busy with today?

368
00:17:24,350 --> 00:17:25,030
Here you go.

369
00:17:25,030 --> 00:17:25,740
Thank you.

370
00:17:27,630 --> 00:17:30,630
I went to Lu Xingyan's inn today.

371
00:17:31,310 --> 00:17:34,070
Zhang Xu wanted
to invite him to join our show.

372
00:17:34,220 --> 00:17:36,660
He came by the office this morning

373
00:17:36,660 --> 00:17:39,070
to talk to us about the promotion
of the resort.

374
00:17:39,070 --> 00:17:42,180
Oh, my God. Isn't that rubbing salt
in your wounds?

375
00:17:43,630 --> 00:17:44,700
What did Lu Xingyan say?

376
00:17:44,980 --> 00:17:45,830
Did he say yes?

377
00:17:47,390 --> 00:17:48,590
He rejected me.

378
00:17:49,740 --> 00:17:51,110
I'm glad he did.

379
00:17:51,790 --> 00:17:52,630
No.

380
00:17:52,790 --> 00:17:55,700
He's our only choice right now.

381
00:17:57,070 --> 00:18:00,550
Well, you have to look
on the bright side of things.

382
00:18:00,740 --> 00:18:03,900
The fact that he's willing to go
to your office to talk to you

383
00:18:04,070 --> 00:18:06,350
proves that he's still
got ideas about this.

384
00:18:06,550 --> 00:18:08,740
You can just talk to him
about cooperation,

385
00:18:08,740 --> 00:18:09,660
not feelings.

386
00:18:11,940 --> 00:18:13,110
But I think

387
00:18:13,220 --> 00:18:15,070
Lu Xingyan has a girlfriend.

388
00:18:15,140 --> 00:18:17,660
He doesn't fit the criteria of our show.

389
00:18:17,980 --> 00:18:19,180
No way.

390
00:18:19,460 --> 00:18:21,660
Did you hear Xu Chengzhou talk about it?

391
00:18:25,110 --> 00:18:26,030
I think

392
00:18:26,030 --> 00:18:28,460
his relationship
with Zhai Jiajing is not simple.

393
00:18:28,700 --> 00:18:30,870
I saw them this afternoon.

394
00:18:30,900 --> 00:18:31,940
They looked

395
00:18:32,550 --> 00:18:34,110
very intimate.

396
00:18:34,700 --> 00:18:35,790
I remember now.

397
00:18:36,220 --> 00:18:38,660
I think Xu Chengzhou
mentioned it to me once before.

398
00:18:38,900 --> 00:18:39,940
Zhai Jiajing

399
00:18:39,940 --> 00:18:42,700
is the legal advisor of their resort.

400
00:18:42,900 --> 00:18:43,550
Legal...

401
00:18:43,550 --> 00:18:45,350
Lu Xingyan sent her to the airport

402
00:18:45,350 --> 00:18:48,550
to explain the bet.

403
00:18:48,640 --> 00:18:50,720
I don't think there's anything going on
between them.

404
00:18:51,830 --> 00:18:52,630
No way.

405
00:18:52,740 --> 00:18:54,900
I don't think this is something
I can just guess at.

406
00:18:55,250 --> 00:18:57,180
I'm going to find a way
to get to the bottom of this.

407
00:18:58,980 --> 00:18:59,790
Dig in.

408
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:11,080
(Aunt Pei)

409
00:19:12,070 --> 00:19:12,940
Answer it.

410
00:19:13,070 --> 00:19:15,270
God has created an opportunity for you

411
00:19:15,630 --> 00:19:17,980
to ask whether Lu Xingyan
has a girlfriend or not.

412
00:19:23,630 --> 00:19:24,790
Xingruo is here.

413
00:19:26,030 --> 00:19:26,700
Xingruo.

414
00:19:27,110 --> 00:19:27,870
Uncle Lu.

415
00:19:28,350 --> 00:19:29,350
Come on in.

416
00:19:31,240 --> 00:19:32,070
Change into slippers.

417
00:19:32,220 --> 00:19:34,110
It's been a long time
since I've seen you.

418
00:19:34,350 --> 00:19:35,310
Long time no see,

419
00:19:35,310 --> 00:19:36,830
You still like fishing so much?

420
00:19:37,070 --> 00:19:38,500
It's my only hobby.

421
00:19:39,460 --> 00:19:40,900
Well, I'm not talking to you today.

422
00:19:40,900 --> 00:19:42,390
My friends are waiting for me.

423
00:19:42,790 --> 00:19:43,790
I'll cook you fish myself

424
00:19:43,790 --> 00:19:45,660
when you come back next time.

425
00:19:45,740 --> 00:19:47,870
I can cook fish very well now.

426
00:19:48,180 --> 00:19:48,980
No problem.

427
00:19:49,550 --> 00:19:51,500
Okay, enjoy. Your Aunt Pei is inside.

428
00:19:51,790 --> 00:19:53,220
Okay, drive safe.

429
00:19:53,220 --> 00:19:53,980
Okay.

430
00:19:54,870 --> 00:19:55,630
Bye.

431
00:20:54,500 --> 00:20:55,310
Aunt Pei.

432
00:20:56,700 --> 00:20:58,940
If I hadn't seen
Chen Zhu's divorce video,

433
00:20:59,350 --> 00:21:01,270
I'd have thought you were still abroad.

434
00:21:02,550 --> 00:21:03,630
You're so ungrateful.

435
00:21:04,180 --> 00:21:05,460
You've been back for two years

436
00:21:05,700 --> 00:21:07,270
and you haven't called me.

437
00:21:07,590 --> 00:21:09,660
If you don't want
to see that brat, that's fine.

438
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:11,420
Don't you want to see me too?

439
00:21:13,220 --> 00:21:13,980
Aunt Pei,

440
00:21:14,870 --> 00:21:15,870
I'm sorry.

441
00:21:17,420 --> 00:21:19,270
If you really want to apologise to me,

442
00:21:19,980 --> 00:21:21,870
then stay with me tonight.

443
00:21:22,740 --> 00:21:24,900
I've been saving that room
of yours for you.

444
00:21:25,420 --> 00:21:26,350
Come on, sit down.

445
00:21:26,590 --> 00:21:27,940
Let me take a good look at you.

446
00:21:30,740 --> 00:21:32,420
Okay? Stay here.

447
00:21:33,140 --> 00:21:34,270
Don't worry.

448
00:21:34,420 --> 00:21:35,870
Just stay here.

449
00:21:35,940 --> 00:21:37,390
Lu Xingyan won't come back.

450
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:39,460
He moved to the inn a long time ago.

451
00:21:40,030 --> 00:21:41,420
We don't see him at home

452
00:21:41,630 --> 00:21:43,550
until the holidays.

453
00:21:44,420 --> 00:21:45,940
It's been so many years.

454
00:21:46,140 --> 00:21:47,630
I've missed you so much.

455
00:21:47,740 --> 00:21:50,180
I've missed you, too. But I...

456
00:21:50,220 --> 00:21:52,660
I know. You two broke up.

457
00:21:52,900 --> 00:21:54,220
That's between you.

458
00:21:54,550 --> 00:21:56,030
It doesn't affect us.

459
00:21:56,490 --> 00:21:58,750
The three of us are independent
individuals who don't affect each other.

460
00:22:01,030 --> 00:22:02,030
But I...

461
00:22:05,110 --> 00:22:06,180
I know.

462
00:22:06,740 --> 00:22:07,870
It's okay.

463
00:22:10,310 --> 00:22:12,180
Anyway, I'm used to being on my own

464
00:22:12,830 --> 00:22:15,310
for a few years
while you're out of the country.

465
00:22:17,270 --> 00:22:19,420
I don't know if it's menopause lately.

466
00:22:21,590 --> 00:22:24,140
Every day when I look
at this empty room,

467
00:22:25,420 --> 00:22:27,070
I feel depressed

468
00:22:28,550 --> 00:22:30,460
in my heart,

469
00:22:33,180 --> 00:22:35,700
and I can't stop my tears from falling.

470
00:22:39,650 --> 00:22:42,230
I can't help but feel my nose
getting sore just talking about it.

471
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:47,070
Ruo, don't mind it.

472
00:22:48,830 --> 00:22:50,180
It's menopause.

473
00:22:51,810 --> 00:22:53,610
I'll just get over it.

474
00:22:55,220 --> 00:22:56,870
It's okay. It's all right.

475
00:22:59,390 --> 00:23:00,830
I won't force you.

476
00:23:00,900 --> 00:23:02,550
You don't have to feel bad about it.

477
00:23:16,420 --> 00:23:17,270
Aunt Pei,

478
00:23:18,590 --> 00:23:20,220
actually, I came here today

479
00:23:20,830 --> 00:23:22,270
to keep you company.

480
00:23:27,310 --> 00:23:29,700
You're the sweetest girl
I've ever known.

481
00:23:30,220 --> 00:23:31,660
I've missed you so much.

482
00:23:31,830 --> 00:23:33,140
Come on, let's have some fruits.

483
00:23:33,740 --> 00:23:34,740
Let's go and watch TV.

484
00:23:34,740 --> 00:23:35,830
Let's watch TV.

485
00:23:35,840 --> 00:23:38,220
That variety show I like
is just about to be updated today.

486
00:23:38,220 --> 00:23:38,980
Come on.

487
00:23:40,420 --> 00:23:41,900
Come on, let's have some fruits.

488
00:24:00,700 --> 00:24:01,420
Is that so?

489
00:24:01,630 --> 00:24:03,270
That's the kind of show you do.

490
00:24:03,550 --> 00:24:04,630
So is it on TV soon?

491
00:24:04,900 --> 00:24:05,900
Not yet.

492
00:24:05,900 --> 00:24:07,220
We've been looking for guests lately.

493
00:24:07,220 --> 00:24:08,790
I'm worried about that.

494
00:24:10,790 --> 00:24:13,500
Do you think Lu Xingyan is suitable?

495
00:24:13,500 --> 00:24:14,230
The door has been opened.

496
00:24:15,980 --> 00:24:17,980
He's not a bad choice

497
00:24:17,980 --> 00:24:20,270
for the dating market, right?

498
00:24:20,630 --> 00:24:22,220
Can he be your guest?

499
00:24:22,830 --> 00:24:25,220
Aunt Pei, the requirements for guests

500
00:24:25,350 --> 00:24:27,740
in a romance variety show
are quite high.

501
00:24:27,900 --> 00:24:30,030
Especially being single,

502
00:24:30,140 --> 00:24:31,550
it's our mandatory requirement.

503
00:24:32,980 --> 00:24:34,660
Then he's a perfect candidate.

504
00:24:34,740 --> 00:24:36,220
Since he broke up with you,

505
00:24:36,220 --> 00:24:38,660
he has put all his thoughts
into the resort.

506
00:24:38,940 --> 00:24:40,660
What's that saying?

507
00:24:41,140 --> 00:24:41,940
Right,

508
00:24:42,590 --> 00:24:46,310
he works every day
to numb the pain of his breakup.

509
00:24:46,590 --> 00:24:47,940
Let me put it to you this way.

510
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:49,970
In the past few years
since you broke up with him,

511
00:24:49,980 --> 00:24:51,940
besides Xu Chengzhou,

512
00:24:51,950 --> 00:24:53,930
he's only been hanging out
with the staff at the resort.

513
00:24:54,350 --> 00:24:56,980
He's always been chaste

514
00:24:57,290 --> 00:24:58,830
and has never been with any other women.

515
00:25:01,550 --> 00:25:02,350
Madam Pei,

516
00:25:02,940 --> 00:25:04,500
if you're drunk, go inside and sleep.

517
00:25:05,420 --> 00:25:07,870
Don't talk nonsense
in front of outsiders.

518
00:25:09,790 --> 00:25:11,180
What brings you home?

519
00:25:13,630 --> 00:25:15,630
You sent me a message
saying something's wrong.

520
00:25:15,950 --> 00:25:17,270
You didn't pick up when I called.

521
00:25:17,420 --> 00:25:18,790
Why do you think I came back?

522
00:25:19,550 --> 00:25:22,140
It's a mistake. I don't know
how to use my new phone,

523
00:25:22,150 --> 00:25:23,110
so I sent the wrong messages.

524
00:25:23,180 --> 00:25:24,460
I see you're doing just fine.

525
00:25:24,790 --> 00:25:25,590
I'm leaving.

526
00:25:26,070 --> 00:25:26,590
Stop there.

527
00:25:29,420 --> 00:25:30,270
I'm drunk.

528
00:25:30,590 --> 00:25:31,790
I just drank too much.

529
00:25:31,830 --> 00:25:33,070
I can't drive.

530
00:25:33,590 --> 00:25:34,420
Lu Xingyan,

531
00:25:35,070 --> 00:25:36,350
take Ruo home for me.

532
00:25:36,590 --> 00:25:38,070
No, I'll just go back myself.

533
00:25:38,220 --> 00:25:39,590
It's late. It's not safe.

534
00:25:39,980 --> 00:25:41,310
She can take a bus.

535
00:25:43,550 --> 00:25:44,940
You won't take her home, huh?

536
00:25:46,660 --> 00:25:47,310
Aunt Pei,

537
00:25:47,900 --> 00:25:48,940
I don't think

538
00:25:49,350 --> 00:25:51,460
he's available to take me home now.

539
00:25:52,500 --> 00:25:54,310
About the show you mentioned,

540
00:25:56,740 --> 00:25:58,790
he doesn't seem
to fit our mandatory requirement.

541
00:25:59,350 --> 00:26:01,180
What... What do you mean by that?

542
00:26:02,980 --> 00:26:04,420
Are you in love?

543
00:26:05,180 --> 00:26:06,070
It can't be.

544
00:26:06,310 --> 00:26:07,630
Aren't you still thinking of Ruo?

545
00:26:07,630 --> 00:26:09,550
I'll take her home.

546
00:26:13,460 --> 00:26:14,180
Producer Shen,

547
00:26:14,870 --> 00:26:15,500
let's go.

548
00:26:34,630 --> 00:26:36,550
We're in the neighborhood.
Just pull over here.

549
00:26:40,630 --> 00:26:41,870
Forget about

