661
00:33:27,110 --> 00:33:27,900
Lu Xingyan,

662
00:33:28,240 --> 00:33:29,940
we've known each other
for so many years.

663
00:33:30,650 --> 00:33:32,030
If you really want
to know the answer,

664
00:33:32,030 --> 00:33:33,830
