671
00:33:56,930 --> 00:33:58,940
But I've noticed
that she doesn't seem to want to.

672
00:34:00,700 --> 00:34:01,220
Yes.

673
00:34:01,220 --> 00:34:03,530
When it comes to relationships,
whoever makes the first move loses.

674
00:34:04,660 --> 00:34:06,660
I don't really care
about winning or losing.

675
00:34:08,660 --> 00:34:09,900
I'm afraid

676
00:34:11,700 --> 00:34:13,750
