and aggressive,

677
00:34:14,270 --> 00:34:15,670
I'll push her away again.

678
00:34:17,610 --> 00:34:19,270
After getting along
with her a few times,

679
00:34:19,670 --> 00:34:21,100
I realised that we're back

680
00:34:21,100 --> 00:34:22,420
to being normal friends again.

681
00:34:25,270 --> 00:34:26,750
That's good, actually.

682
00:34:27,310 --> 00:34:28,150
Good?

683
00:34:28,710 --> 00:34:29,580
Fine.

