00:34:29,590 --> 00:34:32,220
In the vast wide world, your happiness
is the most important thing.

685
00:34:32,980 --> 00:34:33,900
Do whatever you want.

686
00:34:34,610 --> 00:34:35,870
I wonder what Shen Xingruo would think

687
00:34:35,870 --> 00:34:37,020
