to have a talk with us?

736
00:36:51,390 --> 00:36:52,820
Why would the audience want to see us?

737
00:36:52,900 --> 00:36:54,190
Watching us fight?

738
00:36:54,350 --> 00:36:56,310
Or watching us

739
00:36:56,310 --> 00:36:58,060
